cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and deep learning methods for mapping clinical notes to medical codes. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper evaluates the performance of deep learning methods for the task. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated code assignment using machine learning methods. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with mapping clinical notes to medical codes, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a less likely category, but it is possible as the paper deals with the use of technology in the healthcare industry.
